#. type: Title ==
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Why Elasticsearch only?"
msgstr "Por que apenas Elasticsearch?"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Hibernate Search supports both a Lucene backend and an Elasticsearch backend."
msgstr "O Hibernate Search suporta tanto um backend Lucene quanto um backend Elasticsearch."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In the context of Quarkus and to build scalable applications, we thought the latter would make more sense.\n"
"Thus, we focused our efforts on it."
msgstr "No contexto do Quarkus e para construir aplicações escaláveis, pensamos que o último faria mais sentido. Portanto, focamos nossos esforços nele."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We don't have plans to support the Lucene backend in Quarkus for now,\n"
"though there is an issue tracking progress on such an implementation in the Quarkiverse:\n"
"https://github.com/quarkiverse/quarkus-hibernate-search-extras/issues/179[quarkiverse/quarkus-hibernate-search-extras#179]."
msgstr "Não temos planos de suportar o backend Lucene no Quarkus por enquanto, embora haja uma issue acompanhando o progresso de tal implementação no Quarkiverse: https://github.com/quarkiverse/quarkus-hibernate-search-extras/issues/179[quarkiverse/quarkus-hibernate-search-extras#179]."

